  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ABOUT</h2>Defend against the creatures of that night! Protect yourself and your lamp by building and upgrading your base. Equip yourself with the best weapons to deal with the incoming waves.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142610/extras/dd51d5aa8d564b40eb97aa99db260a6a.poster.avif?t=1665930176\" width=706 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142610/extras/dd51d5aa8d564b40eb97aa99db260a6a.webm?t=1665930176\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142610/extras/dd51d5aa8d564b40eb97aa99db260a6a.mp4?t=1665930176\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BUILD</h2>Build a base to defend your base against the incoming creatures. You get a variety of choices on what to add to your base.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142610/extras/b1074ceb4abf5436a8d2b232e8aa6c3f.poster.avif?t=1665930176\" width=706 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142610/extras/b1074ceb4abf5436a8d2b232e8aa6c3f.webm?t=1665930176\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142610/extras/b1074ceb4abf5436a8d2b232e8aa6c3f.mp4?t=1665930176\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >UPGRADE</h2>Upgrade your walls and turrets because the creatures get stronger the longer you last!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142610/extras/c75dd3bb1c5020b987feebdcb140f6ce.poster.avif?t=1665930176\" wi